{"tha-ap340:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap340:0.2":"Gandhodakavagga ","tha-ap340:0.3":"Uttareyyadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap340:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap340:1.2":"ahosim brahmano tada; ","tha-ap340:1.3":"Ajjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap340:1.4":"tinnam vedana paragu. ","tha-ap340:2.1":"Purakkhato sasissehi, ","tha-ap340:2.2":"jatima ca susikkhito; ","tha-ap340:2.3":"Toyabhisecanatthaya, ","tha-ap340:2.4":"nagara nikkhamim tada. ","tha-ap340:3.1":"Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap340:3.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap340:3.3":"Khinasavasahassehi, ","tha-ap340:3.4":"pavisi nagaram jino. ","tha-ap340:4.1":"Sucarurupam disvana, ","tha-ap340:4.2":"anenjakaritam viya; ","tha-ap340:4.3":"Parivutam arahantehi, ","tha-ap340:4.4":"disva cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap340:5.1":"Sirasmim anjalim katva, ","tha-ap340:5.2":"namassitvana subbatam; ","tha-ap340:5.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap340:5.4":"uttariyamadasaham. ","tha-ap340:6.1":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap340:6.2":"satakam ukkhipim aham; ","tha-ap340:6.3":"Yavata buddhaparisa, ","tha-ap340:6.4":"tava chadesi satako. ","tha-ap340:7.1":"Pindacaram carantassa, ","tha-ap340:7.2":"mahabhikkhuganadino; ","tha-ap340:7.3":"Chadam karonto atthasi, ","tha-ap340:7.4":"hasayanto mamam tada. ","tha-ap340:8.1":"Gharato nikkhamantassa, ","tha-ap340:8.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap340:8.3":"Vithiyamva thito sattha, ","tha-ap340:8.4":"aka me anumodanam. ","tha-ap340:9.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap340:9.2":"yo me adasi satakam; ","tha-ap340:9.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap340:9.4":"sunotha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap340:10.1":"‘Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap340:10.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap340:10.3":"Pannasakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap340:10.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap340:11.1":"Devaloke vasantassa, ","tha-ap340:11.2":"punnakammasamangino; ","tha-ap340:11.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","tha-ap340:11.4":"dussacchannam bhavissati. ","tha-ap340:12.1":"Chattimsakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap340:12.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap340:12.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap340:12.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap340:13.1":"Bhave samsaramanassa, ","tha-ap340:13.2":"punnakammasamangino; ","tha-ap340:13.3":"Manasa patthitam sabbam, ","tha-ap340:13.4":"nibbattissati tavade. ","tha-ap340:14.1":"Koseyyakambaliyani, ","tha-ap340:14.2":"khomakappasikani ca; ","tha-ap340:14.3":"Mahagghani ca dussani, ","tha-ap340:14.4":"patilacchatiyam naro. ","tha-ap340:15.1":"Manasa patthitam sabbam, ","tha-ap340:15.2":"patilacchatiyam naro; ","tha-ap340:15.3":"Ekadussassa vipakam, ","tha-ap340:15.4":"anubhossati sabbada. ","tha-ap340:16.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap340:16.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap340:16.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap340:16.4":"dhammam sacchikarissati’. ","tha-ap340:17.1":"Aho me sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap340:17.2":"sabbannussa mahesino; ","tha-ap340:17.3":"Ekaham satakam datva, ","tha-ap340:17.4":"pattomhi amatam padam. ","tha-ap340:18.1":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","tha-ap340:18.2":"vasato sunnake ghare; ","tha-ap340:18.3":"Dhareti dussachadanam, ","tha-ap340:18.4":"samanta byamato mama. ","tha-ap340:19.1":"Avinnattam nivasemi, ","tha-ap340:19.2":"civaram paccayancaham; ","tha-ap340:19.3":"Labhi annassa panassa, ","tha-ap340:19.4":"uttareyyassidam phalam. ","tha-ap340:20.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap340:20.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap340:20.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap340:20.4":"vatthadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap340:21.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap340:21.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap340:21.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap340:22.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma uttareyyadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap340:23.1":"Uttareyyadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}